                         default='any2any,any2dif,any2spe', type=str,
                         help='default=%(default)s: Comma-delimited combinatorial-substitution statistics '
                              'to compute and report. Choose from '
                              'any2any, any2spe, any2dif, dif2any, dif2spe, dif2dif, '
